text: "Which of the following statements about Palonosetron are incorrect:",
options: [{"id": "A", "text": "It is a second generation 5HT3 receptor antagonist", "is_correct": false}, {"id": "B", "text": "It belongs to the class of most effective drugs for chemotherapy induced nausea and vomiting", "is_correct": false}, {"id": "C", "text": "It is the longest acting drug amongst its class", "is_correct": false}, {"id": "D", "text": "High risk of QT prolongation as adverse reaction", "is_correct": true}],
